      <li class="mb-2"><a href="#" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Akismet: Version 4.0.2 of the Akismet RailPress Plugin Is Now Available</a></li>
      <li class="mb-2"><a href="#" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">WPTavern: Jetpack 5.6.1 Increases Security of the Contact Form Module</a></li>
      <li class="mb-2"><a href="#" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">WPWeekly Episode 297 â€“ WordCamp US 2017 Recap</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
